text:
I am building a custom workflow action that contains both remote option inputs and static inputs.  Sample input fields are below. It all functions, but I notice that when I am using the workflow editor and type into the static text input field `textfield`, a remote call is being made to  re-obtain the available options for the `remoteOption` field. There are no dependencies between the fields. It just seems strange and unnecessary to have the system make these remote calls every single time I type a character into another input field.  *Is this normal behavior?* 

```      {
        typeDefinition: {
          name: 'remoteOption',
          type: 'enumeration',
          fieldType: 'select',
          optionsUrl: `https://${host}/v1/action/options`
        },
        supportedValueTypes: 'STATIC_VALUE',
        isRequired: true
      },
      {
        typeDefinition: {
          name: 'textfield',
          type: 'string',
          fieldType: 'text'
        },
        supportedValueTypes: 'STATIC_VALUE',
        isRequired: true
      }```
